Title: New Squid Game Operators & Skins | CALL OF DUTY BLACK OPS 6
Description: Get ready for an epic crossover as Squid Game takes over Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 and Warzone! This special event marks the release of Squid Game Season 2, delivering heart-pounding action and suspense straight from the Netflix series into your favorite first-person shooter. Whether you're a fan of Squid Game, Call of Duty, or both, this collaboration is packed with exclusive content and rewards you don’t want to miss.  🎮 Explore Squid Game Operators Play as iconic characters like the Pink Guards, Masked VIPs, and the eerie yet unforgettable Young-Hee doll. From their detailed skins to unique animations and voice lines, these Operators bring Squid Game’s tense atmosphere to every match.  💥 Event Pass Rewards for Every Player Take part in the Squid Game 2 Event Pass to unlock amazing rewards, including:  Free Rewards: Instantly claim the Player 006 Operator Skin for Niran when you access the Event Pass. Earned Rewards: Grind through the Free Track to unlock the Player 115 Operator Skin by earning 76,000 XP. Premium Rewards: Upgrade to the Premium Pass for 1,100 Call of Duty Points and work your way to the ultimate prize—the Front Man Operator Skin, earned with 356,000 XP. 🛒 Themed Bundles in the Store Squid Game-themed bundles offer even more customization options to enhance your experience:  Pink Guards Tracer Pack: Features the Masked Worker, Soldier, and Manager skins, along with weapon blueprints, calling cards, reticles, and more. The VIPs Tracer Pack: Luxurious gold-themed Panther and Lion Masked VIP skins, exclusive weapon blueprints, and elegant cosmetics. Young-Hee Tracer Pack: The animatronic doll comes to life with toy-themed blueprints, sprays, decals, and other chilling cosmetics. 🔥 Custom Skins, Weapons, and More Equip unique blueprints like the Rule Master Assault Rifle, Satin Slayer SMG, or the Death Plated Frag Skin, and make your loadout stand out in every game. Bring the high-stakes tension of Squid Game to your battles with dramatic finishing moves like Winner and Pinky Up.  🌟 Why You Can’t Miss This Event This is more than just a collaboration—it's a celebration of two iconic franchises combining their strengths. Whether you're competing in Warzone or dominating multiplayer in Black Ops 6, the Squid Game event adds a thrilling new layer to the gameplay. Plus, the nostalgic nods to the show make it a treat for fans!  🕹️ It’s Your Turn to Survive the Games So, what are you waiting for? Jump into the action, complete challenges, unlock exclusive rewards, and experience the thrill of Squid Game in the world of Call of Duty.
